Render document pages to PNG images on disk

Usage: udoc render [OPTIONS] --output <DIR> <FILE>

Arguments:
  <FILE>  Input document

Options:
  -o, --output <DIR>   Output directory. Created if missing
  -p, --pages <PAGES>  Page range (e.g. "1-5", "3,7,9-12"). Renders every page when omitted
      --dpi <DPI>      Render DPI [default: 300]
  -h, --help           Print help
